### =====================================================
### CUSTOMER API - TESTS AVANCÉS ET CAS LIMITES
### =====================================================
### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### =====================================================
### 🧪 TESTS DE VALIDATION
### =====================================================

### TEST - Email déjà existant (doublon - erreur probable)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Duplicate",
  "lastName": "Email",
  "email": "jean.dupont@example.com"
}

### TEST - Champ firstName vide
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": "Test",
  "email": "test.empty@example.com"
}

### TEST - Champ lastName vide
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "",
  "email": "test.lastname@example.com"
}

### TEST - Email invalide (sans @)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "Invalid",
  "email": "test.invalid.email"
}

### =====================================================
### 📊 TESTS AVEC DONNÉES COMPLEXES
### =====================================================

### TEST - Customer avec caractères spéciaux
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "François",
  "lastName": "D'Orléans",
  "email": "francois.dorleans@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+33 1 23 45 67 89",
  "address": "123 Rue de l'École",
  "city": "Île-de-France",
  "postalCode": "75000",
  "country": "France"
}

### TEST - Customer avec données très longues
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Alexandre",
  "lastName": "Van Der Something Very Long Name",
  "email": "very.long.email.address.that.is.quite.extended@very-long-domain-name.example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "0123456789012345",
  "address": "Very Long Street Address Number 123 Building A Apartment 4567",
  "city": "VeryLongCityNameThatIsMostlyForTesting",
  "postalCode": "123456",
  "country": "Very Long Country Name"
}

### TEST - Customer international
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "José",
  "lastName": "García",
  "email": "jose.garcia@example.es",
  "phoneNumber": "+34 912 345 678",
  "address": "Calle Mayor 123",
  "city": "Madrid",
  "postalCode": "28001",
  "country": "España"
}

### =====================================================
### 🔍 TESTS DE RECHERCHE
### =====================================================

### GET - Vérifier tous les customers créés
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Accept: {{contentType}}

###
### GET - Chercher par différents emails
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/email/francois.dorleans@example.com
Accept: {{contentType}}

###
### GET - Email non trouvé
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/email/nonexistent@example.com
Accept: {{contentType}}

### =====================================================
